cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this benchmark, please cite it as below."
title: "quant-bench: a fair speed/accuracy/memory benchmark of LLM weight quantization"
authors:
  - family-names: "Mimouni"
    given-names: "A."
repository-code: "https://github.com/Tomahawk888/llm-quant-bench"
license: CC-BY-4.0
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-06-25"
keywords: [LLM, quantization, benchmark, AWQ, AQLM, GPU, perplexity]
abstract: >
  Reproducible single-GPU benchmark of LLM weight-quantization methods measured
  under one HuggingFace forward harness: decode throughput, prefill latency, peak
  VRAM and full wikitext-2 perplexity. Measured on H100 for Llama-2 7B and 70B.
